      "source_text": "1 本項披露中，賬面總值指未就任何虧損準備作調整之金融資產已攤銷成本。上表所示按公允值計入其他全面收益之債務工具的賬面總值不包括公允值損益，因此不會與資產負債表所示數額一致。",
      "translation_target_text": "1 In this disclosure, gross carrying value refers to the amortized cost of the financial asset before any adjustment for loss provisions. The total carrying amount of debt instruments at fair value through other comprehensive income shown in the table above does not include fair value gains and losses and therefore will not be consistent with the amounts shown on the balance sheet.",
      "translation_en": "1 In this disclosure, gross carrying value refers to the amortized cost of the financial asset before any adjustment for loss provisions. The total carrying amount of debt instruments at fair value through other comprehensive income shown in the table above does not include fair value gains and losses and therefore will not be consistent with the amounts shown on the balance sheet.",
